34
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,520
(Might as well accept her)

35
00:02:16,919 --> 00:02:18,599
(and drive Lin Chuning away first)

36
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,240
(before handling the rest.)

37
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,280
Kneel.

38
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,120
