with Father and Mother.

45
00:02:39,479 --> 00:02:41,159
I'm sorry. I didn't mean it.

46
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:44,840
Silly girl.

47
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,560
You've done nothing wrong.

48
00:02:46,759 --> 00:02:48,280
She's the one who wronged you.

49
00:02:48,948 --> 00:02:49,640
You're

50
