59
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,319
Regret?

60
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,400
When you pushed me into the river,

61
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:16,080
when you kept shouting

62
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:18,159
that you'd kill your own daughter,

63
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,919
I didn't see even a trace of regret.

64
00:03:25,131 --> 00:03:25,720
Xiaorou.

65
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:27,680
Are you not scared?

66
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,280
The next person she kills

67
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,400
could be you.

68
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,560
Mother.

69
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,920
I already knew you weren't my daughter.

70
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:35,919
I was momentarily furious

71
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:37,200
