72
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:39,319
How could I

73
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:41,280
ever hurt my birth daughter?

74
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,400
Someone, come.

75
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:50,840
Beat her to death

76
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,960
and dump her in the pond.

77
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:01,599
Lu Siyan.

78
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,000
Get lost.

79
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:08,759
Are you rebelling?

80
00:04:09,759 --> 00:04:10,439
Siyan.

81
00:04:10,719 --> 00:04:12,639
She's not your sister. Sober up.

82
00:04:13,159 --> 00:04:14,800
I wish she weren't my sister.

83
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,040
Mother.

84
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,959
Have you forgotten

85
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:31,759
