86
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,160
to protect her for me?

87
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,920
Don't let anyone hurt her.

88
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,480
Just because I said nothing

89
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,439
