107
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,079
Fine.

108
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,000
Very well.

109
00:05:17,319 --> 00:05:18,040
Lin Chuning.

110
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,600
