120
00:05:37,879 --> 00:05:39,879
because of me.

121
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,519
Mr. Lu.

122
00:05:42,319 --> 00:05:43,360
If you kill me,

123
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:45,480
