126
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:00,879
Father.

127
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:01,560
Mother.

128
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,639
Chuning grew up all alone.

129
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:06,439
