00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:22,399
who's all talk and no action.

291
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,320
I'll prove with action

292
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:25,919
that only I

293
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,440
can protect Chuning.

294
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,240
Alright.

295
00:13:36,399 --> 00:13:37,919
I ask you

296
00:13:38,519 --> 00:13:39,639
to prove yourself.

297
00:13:42,680 --> 00:13:43,418
What are you doing?

298
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:44,480
Siyan!

299
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:45,159
Don't move!

300
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:46,679
Proved yourself yet?

301
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,120
Siyan.

302
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:59,000
Geese fly side by side across the world.

303
00:13:59,519 --> 00:14:01,879
They're known to be faithful.

304
00:14:02,519 --> 00:14:03,600
One partner

305
00:14:04,039 --> 00:14:05,039
for one lifetime.

306
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:09,320
I've already found my true love.

307
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,320
Mochen.

308
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:14,879
You'll also find yours soon.

309
00:14:15,920 --> 00:14:16,840
You can have this back.

310
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:20,240
Move.

311
00:14:32,639 --> 00:14:33,240
Siyan.

312
00:14:34,039 --> 00:14:34,919
Arms out.

313
00:14:34,919 --> 00:14:36,039
I'll measure you.

314
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:41,039
Jealous?

315
00:14:42,279 --> 00:14:42,679
No.

316
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:47,919
That sour tone sounds jealous.

317
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:48,720
Hurry up.

318
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,960
He came to propose to you.

319
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:52,919
How am I not jealous?

320
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,320
You did that on purpose.

321
00:15:05,679 --> 00:15:06,519
Obviously.

322
00:15:07,759 --> 00:15:08,360
Kiss me.

323
00:15:13,039 --> 00:15:13,720
Happy now?

324
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:14,399
Yes.

325
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:17,320
Lift your arms then.

326
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:17,759
Quick.

327
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:20,720
What are you doing?

328
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:23,879
Secret.

329
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:24,720
I'm not telling you.

330
00:15:29,679 --> 00:15:30,120
Alright.

331
00:15:30,399 --> 00:15:31,000
Turn around.

332
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:41,320
I know!

333
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,353
You're making me clothes.

334
00:15:42,393 --> 00:15:42,993
Right?

335
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:44,000
I knew it.

336
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:44,960
I'll wait for it.

337
00:15:53,159 --> 00:15:53,639
Chuning.

338
00:15:56,159 --> 00:15:56,720
Siyan.

339
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:00,200
Does it look good?

340
00:16:01,039 --> 00:16:02,320
Of course, you made it.

341
00:16:03,900 --> 00:16:05,990
(Lin Chuning)

342
00:16:06,057 --> 00:16:08,908
♪Wanderers who found their way back♪

343
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:10,679
What does this mean?

344
00:16:13,639 --> 00:16:14,679
You know exactly what.

345
00:16:16,520 --> 00:16:17,279
Give me your hand.

346
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:20,600
Can you feel my heartbeat?

347
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:22,039
Yes.

348
00:16:22,039 --> 00:16:23,879
Your heart's beating really fast.

349
00:16:25,800 --> 00:16:27,000
Because you're in my heart.

350
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:27,600
Lu Siyan!

351
00:16:28,159 --> 00:16:29,120
It's time to train.

352
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:29,600
Coming!

353
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:33,560
♪You're the dark snow slowly arriving♪

354
00:16:33,560 --> 00:16:34,520
Ever since I was little,

355
00:16:34,605 --> 00:16:35,400
I dreamed

356
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:37,759
of soaring freely

357
00:16:39,005 --> 00:16:40,057
like a bird

358
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:41,759
through the sky.

359
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:42,759
Back then,

360
00:16:42,759 --> 00:16:44,160
I didn't even know what a pilot was.

361
00:16:44,160 --> 00:16:46,360
When I heard the military academy
was recruiting pilots,

362
00:16:46,759 --> 00:16:48,159
I signed up right away.

363
00:16:48,405 --> 00:16:50,160
At first, it was just for fun.

364
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:53,759
But when I saw enemy planes
flying freely over our skies,

365
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:54,960
I made up my mind

366
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:56,960
to protect this land.

367
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:58,360
One day,

368
00:16:58,679 --> 00:17:00,759
we'll free our country from gloom.

369
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:01,639
Believe me.

370
00:17:02,325 --> 00:17:03,200
I will

371
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:04,839
protect you

372
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,119
and everyone.

373
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:09,388
♪Where millions have been swept away♪

374
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,120
I believe you.

375
00:17:11,485 --> 00:17:14,205
♪I turn into white, pure snow♪

376
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:15,599
Alright.

377
00:17:17,279 --> 00:17:18,039
I'm leaving.

378
00:17:18,131 --> 00:17:23,897
♪Only in your gentle embrace
can I find peace♪

379
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,160
Lu Siyan.

380
00:17:51,839 --> 00:17:52,799
Attention.

381
00:17:54,319 --> 00:17:55,160
About face!

382
00:18:01,474 --> 00:18:05,360
♪Let me look once more♪

383
00:18:05,405 --> 00:18:11,577
♪Let the wind wait for the setting sun♪

384
00:18:11,914 --> 00:18:14,080
♪With you♪

385
00:18:14,211 --> 00:18:18,182
♪I recall the days behind♪

386
00:18:18,245 --> 00:18:24,600
♪When your presence
lit the path I longed to find♪

387
00:18:27,102 --> 00:18:31,051
♪Let it go for now♪

388
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:32,400
Wait for me.

389
00:18:33,520 --> 00:18:34,279
I'll wait for you.

390
00:18:37,531 --> 00:18:39,742
♪Somehow♪

391
00:18:39,862 --> 00:18:43,051
♪And as I reflect with care♪

392
00:18:43,102 --> 00:18:49,634
♪Those meant to meet again
never need to force it♪

393
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:08,680
You showed up uninvited.

394
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:09,880
What do you want?

395
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:14,440
You're Siyan's mother.

396
00:19:14,759 --> 00:19:15,960
That's why I've tolerated you.

397
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:17,519
But that doesn't mean I'm a pushover.

398
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:21,880
I've never thought you were a pushover.

399
00:19:22,360 --> 00:19:24,279
It's alright
that you pretended to be my daughter,

400
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:25,480
but you even seduced my son.

401
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:27,240
Have you looked at yourself?

402
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:29,720
A wild orphan

403
00:19:29,839 --> 00:19:30,880
is worse than a courtesan.

404
00:19:31,360 --> 00:19:33,079
How dare you dream
of marrying into nobility?

405
00:19:33,480 --> 00:19:35,920
You've got my son so bewitched
that he won't even come home.

406
00:19:37,079 --> 00:19:38,119
Mrs. Lu,

407
00:19:38,520 --> 00:19:39,559
you'd better be careful.

408
00:19:40,319 --> 00:19:41,640
Don't let your son

409
00:19:41,839 --> 00:19:42,720
be so bewitched

410
00:19:43,039 --> 00:19:45,599
by a wild orphan like me

411
00:19:45,839 --> 00:19:47,839
that you blame someone else's daughter.

412
00:19:48,119 --> 00:19:49,799
You're still unrepentant
at death's door.

413
00:19:50,599 --> 00:19:52,079
Beautiful woman brings trouble.

414
00:19:52,560 --> 00:19:53,799
Looks like I can't let you stay.

415
00:20:05,799 --> 00:20:07,839
Since Mr. Lu said
to spare your pitiful life,

416
00:20:07,839 --> 00:20:08,880
I won't kill you.

417
00:20:09,279 --> 00:20:10,359
But you must leave.

418
00:20:11,079 --> 00:20:11,920
Whether I die

419
00:20:12,440 --> 00:20:13,480
or run away,

420
00:20:13,799 --> 00:20:15,039
Siyan will hate you.

421
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:18,240
Let him hate me then.

422
00:20:18,880 --> 00:20:19,960
I'm his birth mother.

423
00:20:20,359 --> 00:20:22,160
He won't love you forever,

424
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:23,680
nor will he hate me forever.

425
00:20:42,097 --> 00:20:42,988
Safe travels.

426
00:20:44,594 --> 00:20:46,417
Write me when you arrive.

427
00:20:46,839 --> 00:20:47,359
Need help?

428
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:48,480
No need.

429
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:51,000
This is my wife.
She has trouble walking.

430
00:20:51,120 --> 00:20:52,799
She takes medication
and gets sleepy easily.

431
00:20:56,799 --> 00:20:57,680
I'm home.

432
00:21:02,702 --> 00:21:03,520
Why are you here?

433
00:21:06,799 --> 00:21:07,440
Where's Chuning?

434
00:21:07,759 --> 00:21:08,519
Siyan.

435
00:21:09,080 --> 00:21:10,851
I asked you where Lin Chuning is.

436
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:12,680
You like Sister.

437
00:21:12,828 --> 00:21:13,880
I'm your sister too.

438
00:21:14,542 --> 00:21:15,680
What did you do to her?

439
00:21:15,965 --> 00:21:17,080
I didn't do anything to her.

440
00:21:18,051 --> 00:21:19,360
It's Mother who wants her dead.

441
00:21:20,319 --> 00:21:22,279
You'll never see her again.

442
00:21:22,862 --> 00:21:24,040
The train is about to leave.

443
00:21:27,297 --> 00:21:28,680
Your love will only get her killed!

444
00:21:36,840 --> 00:21:38,422
- Careful.
- Don't worry, it'll be fine.

445
00:21:41,548 --> 00:21:43,137
Don't worry. Go back.

446
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:47,279
Chuning.

447
00:21:47,474 --> 00:21:48,668
Don't forget to bring...

448
00:21:49,519 --> 00:21:49,960
Chuning.

449
00:21:51,440 --> 00:21:52,039
It's me.

450
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:56,720
Help me.

451
00:21:57,279 --> 00:21:57,680
Chuning.

452
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:58,759
I'm here.

453
00:22:01,799 --> 00:22:02,559
Mochen.

454
00:22:03,240 --> 00:22:04,160
Why are you here?

455
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:05,400
Xiaorou said

456
00:22:05,600 --> 00:22:06,640
they were sending you away.

457
00:22:08,119 --> 00:22:09,079
That's why I came.

458
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:09,920
Are you alright?

459
00:22:11,079 --> 00:22:11,680
I'm fine now.

460
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:13,440
Thank god you got here in time.

461
00:22:16,759 --> 00:22:18,480
I've found somewhere very safe.

462
00:22:18,559 --> 00:22:19,960
They won't get a chance

463
00:22:20,542 --> 00:22:21,320
to hurt you again.

464
00:22:22,839 --> 00:22:23,480
Alright?

465
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:25,559
Mochen.

466
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:27,839
I thought I made myself

467
00:22:28,039 --> 00:22:29,440
very clear last time.

468
00:22:30,839 --> 00:22:32,000
But Lu Siyan

469
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:33,720
can't protect you.

470
00:22:34,400 --> 00:22:35,880
Mrs. Lu won't let this go.

471
00:22:36,440 --> 00:22:38,160
Even if you flee to another city,

472
00:22:38,160 --> 00:22:40,079
how can a meek woman like you survive

473
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:41,359
without me or Lu Siyan?

474
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:45,440
Why must I rely on either of you

475
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:46,960
to survive?

476
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:48,720
Chuning!

477
00:22:53,519 --> 00:22:54,200
Chuning!

478
00:22:55,240 --> 00:22:56,000
Lu Siyan.

479
00:22:57,709 --> 00:22:58,349
Chu...

480
00:23:02,119 --> 00:23:02,720
Siyan!

481
00:23:02,720 --> 00:23:03,559
Someone got stabbed.

482
00:23:04,039 --> 00:23:04,720
Siyan!

483
00:23:16,279 --> 00:23:16,680
Siyan.

484
00:23:17,119 --> 00:23:17,839
Siyan.

485
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:19,119
Siyan.

486
00:23:20,240 --> 00:23:21,319
Siyan, wake up.

487
00:23:22,359 --> 00:23:22,920
Siyan!

488
00:23:24,839 --> 00:23:25,720
Help!

489
00:23:26,245 --> 00:23:26,920
Help!

490
00:23:28,319 --> 00:23:28,880
Siyan!

491
00:23:29,799 --> 00:23:30,519
Siyan!

492
00:23:35,400 --> 00:23:36,119
Siyan!

493
00:23:38,640 --> 00:23:39,519
Help!

494
00:23:40,200 --> 00:23:41,480
Someone, help me!

495
00:23:43,519 --> 00:23:44,519
Siyan!

496
00:23:45,119 --> 00:23:46,160
Siyan!

497
00:24:01,990 --> 00:24:04,900
♪Barging into the sea
that bears your name♪

498
00:24:05,310 --> 00:24:07,760
♪Swimming to the end with loneliness♪

499
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:11,150
♪Going against the current
and over the reef traps♪

500
00:24:11,280 --> 00:24:14,370
♪Clearing the fog
just to get close to you♪

501
00:24:15,350 --> 00:24:18,120
♪Pushing away
the gravel hidden beneath the seaweed♪

502
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:21,090
♪Wandering near your heart♪

503
00:24:21,190 --> 00:24:24,720
♪I imagined
our encounter countless times♪

504
00:24:24,900 --> 00:24:27,720
♪So close, yet out of reach♪

505
00:24:28,630 --> 00:24:33,780
♪Keeping
all this lonely courage to myself♪

506
00:24:34,940 --> 00:24:41,110
♪I was never part of your world♪

507
00:24:41,200 --> 00:24:44,730
♪If your silhouette
was etched upon the sea♪

508
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:47,780
♪The sky as your wedding dress♪

509
00:24:47,840 --> 00:24:51,370
♪Turn me into a cloud♪

510
00:24:51,570 --> 00:24:54,490
♪Keep a sliver of the past♪

511
00:24:54,550 --> 00:24:58,210
♪If love is like an illusory bubble♪

512
00:24:58,310 --> 00:25:01,410
♪Together forever in my dreams♪

513
00:25:01,640 --> 00:25:07,140
♪I'd rest forever in your arms♪

