518
00:25:35,350 --> 00:25:38,320
♪Returning to the land
left bare by the receding sea♪

519
00:25:38,500 --> 00:25:41,210
♪Withering like a fallen leaf♪

520
00:25:41,270 --> 00:25:44,720
♪The message in a bottle
buried on the shore♪

521
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:47,720
♪No one asked♪

