531
00:26:27,850 --> 00:26:31,590
♪If the sea didn't wait
for the evening breeze♪

532
00:26:31,660 --> 00:26:34,460
♪And swim with me to you♪

533
00:26:34,510 --> 00:26:38,050
♪I'd become♪

534
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:41,110
♪A whale
who forever keeps the sea company♪

535
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:44,780
♪If love is like a night storm♪

536
00:26:44,920 --> 00:26:48,050
♪Unable to stop for a moment♪

537
